      uid=4_3838 StaticText "中文文档 (Chinese Documentation)"
    uid=4_3839 StaticText "Stop losing context. Stop blocking on tasks. Stop shipping bugs. This battle-tested system turns PRDs into epics, epics into GitHub issues, and issues into production code – with full traceability at every step."
