    uid=4_3876 heading "Background" level="2"
    uid=4_3877 link "Permalink: Background" url="https://github.com/kennyto266/cbsc-system-unification#background"
    uid=4_3878 StaticText "Every team struggles with the same problems:"
    uid=4_3879 StaticText "Context evaporates"
    uid=4_3880 StaticText " between sessions, forcing constant re-discovery"
    uid=4_3881 StaticText "Parallel work creates conflicts"
    uid=4_3882 StaticText " when multiple developers touch the same code"
    uid=4_3883 StaticText "Requirements drift"
    uid=4_3884 StaticText " as verbal decisions override written specs"
    uid=4_3885 StaticText "Progress becomes invisible"
    uid=4_3886 StaticText " until the very end"
    uid=4_3887 StaticText "This system solves all of that."
    uid=4_3888 heading "The Workflow" level="2"
    uid=4_3889 link "Permalink: The Workflow" url="https://github.com/kennyto266/cbsc-system-unification#the-workflow"
